                        <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
                    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <img class="rounded-circle" src="~/Images/Product/eb8c20bf-20e7-4f19-a963-7624ac1ee470.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
                        <h2>Performance Tires</h2>
                        <p>
                            Improved handling and braking performance
                            Enhanced traction and handling
                            Even distribution of contact pressure
                            Improved traction in the wet and low noise emission
                            Enhanced traction and handling.
                        </p>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
                    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <img class="rounded-circle" src="~/Images/Product/52adad9b-86d0-4643-9db9-bae579f0738b.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
                        <h2>Performance Rotors</h2>
                        <p>
                            Dill holes ensure cooler performance.
                            Rounded slots keep away gas, water and dust
                            Higher coefficient of friction than OE
                            Carbon Fiber infused Evolution ceramic formula provides superior braking power.
                        </p>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
                    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                </div><!-- /.row -->
                <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

                <hr class="featurette-divider">

                <div class="row featurette">
                    <div class="col-md-7">
                        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Now Open For Business.<span class="text-muted"> Make your car your own. </span></h2>
                        <p class="lead">Register or login to view custom offers, deals, sales and clearance specials. Immediate shipping available!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5" style="height:40px;">
                        <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="/Images/Company/pexels-pixabay-316149.jpg"   style="height:350px;" alt="Generic placeholder image">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="featurette-divider">

             

               

                <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->

            </div><!-- /.container -->
